### ========================================
### ADMIN REGISTRATION ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### Setup Initial Admin (Public - Only works if no admin exists)
### Use this endpoint FIRST to create the very first admin user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/setup/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "phone_number": "+1234567890",
  "role_id": 1,
  "password": "adminpassword123"
}

### Register a new Admin (Admin only - requires authentication)
### Use this endpoint to create additional admin users (requires existing admin token)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/register/admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Second Admin",
  "email": "admin2@example.com",
  "phone_number": "+1234567895",
  "role_id": 1,
  "password": "adminpassword456"
}

### ========================================
### SUB-ADMIN REGISTRATION
### ========================================

### Register a sub-admin (Admin only - requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/register/sub-admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Jane Admin",
  "email": "jane.admin@example.com",
  "phone_number": "+1234567891",
  "role_id": 2,
  "password": "adminpassword123"
}

